&lt;li&gt;Owning Nova Credit&#39;s technology and product strategy, including setting the vision for our platform across Engineering, Infrastructure, Data Science, and Product &amp;amp; Design, and ensuring alignment with company-wide goals and mission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading transformative, cross-functional initiatives that elevate the reliability, scalability, and strategic impact of our enterprise-grade platform. You’ll also need to zoom in and support the team in our fast-paced development environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving as a connective force across the organization, actively building trust and context between Build and every other function, so that engineering, product and analytics priorities stay aligned and the business operates as a cohesive whole&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying where AI creates durable competitive advantage in our products and where it can meaningfully accelerate how our teams build, ship, and operate, and helping your organization act on both&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving as an expert coach, mentor, and empathetic leader to a team of managers across each function, fostering a culture of continuous growth, and both hard and soft skill development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making high-stakes decisions that shape the organization&#39;s long-term success, navigating complex tradeoffs with sound judgment and a transformative mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Representing Nova Credit externally as a thought leader, communicating our technical and product philosophy to customers, partners, regulators, and the broader industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruiting, developing, and retaining talent and coaching your managers to do the same within their teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
